<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" style="padding-top: 20px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
      <h1>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h1>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0;">
        Your project <strong><%= @post.title %></strong> has been declined!<br>
        This means something was incorrect in your submition and will require changes before it can be approved.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>The following reason was given:</strong>

        <div style="padding-top: 20px; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 20px; background-color: #fff">
          <%= simple_format @description %>
        </div>
      </p>
      <p>
        Please refer to the feedback and try again. Contact us if you are unsure about any of the comments we have given.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
